Placeholder Recurring Encounter

Something happens! In the further swamp.

choices:

* Negotiate = Try to convince them
    @if check negotiation easy {
      You convince them!
      +heal_spirits small
      +give_gold small
    } @else {
      You fail!
      +rem_gold small
      +damage_spirits small
    }

* Fight = Do the ultimate punchies
    @if check combat easy {
        You win!
        +heal_spirits small
        +give_gold small
    } @else {
        You lose!
        +damage_health small
        +damage_spirits small
    }

* Sneak = Use big sneaky skills
    @if check cunning easy {
        You win!
        +heal_spirits small
        +give_gold small
    } @else {
        You lose!
        +damage_health small
